name: San La Muerte / Say your prayers
description:
He decides if you are worthy of the love you let slip away, he decides when your enemy will come repentant at your feet, how much you’ll win in that bet, what punishment he will impart to those who have harmed you.

This piece is part of my contribution to "Our Myths" event held by Chen >>> https://www.hicetnunc.xyz/objkt/365336
